This is how to search of lst:
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this lst's length times:
      Remember that count is 0
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this lst's length times:
         When item j in lst is item i in lst, then:
            Increase count
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      When count is 2, then:
         The answer is item i in lst
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is -1
